{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"马尔加什谚语","authors":["丁岐江"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"马尔加什谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△若是大家都走到河里，鳄鱼不敢张嘴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△家鼠和田鼠长得一样，却不是同住一个地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△植物虽多，只有甘蔗甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△奴隶歌唱不是因为欢乐，而是饥饿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△友谊不能买——要靠忠诚去换来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△虚伪的朋友，背信弃义也不觉得害羞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△和坏人交朋友，他本身就不是真正的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔丁岐江译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}